 />\n 另一方面，大麻、大麻樹脂及若干種大麻素(包括四氫大麻酚 (THC)及大麻酚(CBN))均屬受《危險藥物條例》管制的危險 藥物。"},{"pid":"34acaed49af6c93b6535811d23ed65db43c2e601","tid":2451292,"uid":40292,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b32ccd93d47de848756bf691ed25066b7351534","tid":2451292,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"死道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大麻一定會令人上癮，害撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:08:46.000Z","msg":"唔介意你反吸食大麻<br />\n但你唔知咩係CBD就縮返入老母閪到先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629bd3449260057ecfa037a42198ab617d986c23","tid":2451292,"uid":149662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7954594a8796031496ff5d62a755da0d90ce6eb3","tid":2451292,"uid":79793,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"0f25245c1fa7e84658ca776f303dd5b09ca63a38","tid":2451292,"uid":149662,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"8b32ccd93d47de848756bf691ed25066b7351534","tid":2451292,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T04:01:42.000Z","msg":"死道友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大麻一定會令人上癮，害撚死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 